extendedInfo.description: Mobile posing reference guide for photographers that gives ideas for poses & angles. App contains tons of great pro photos. Save & edit your faves and look thru them so you know what images you'd like to add to your portfolio.And check out our other posing apps: Baby, Child, Siblings, Couples, Maternity, Models, Wedding
